STREAM_API_KEY=your_stream_api_key
STREAM_SECRET_KEY=your_stream_secret_key

NEXT_PUBLIC_STREAM_API_KEY=your_stream_api_key



# ========================== Steps to Get Stream API Key & Secret =====================================
# 1. Sign Up / Log In
# Go to https://getstream.io/
# Click Sign up or Log in.



# 2. =========================== Create an App ============================
# Once logged in:

# Go to your dashboard

# Click “Create App”

# Fill in:

# App Name (e.g., LawCrew Chat)

# Server Location (e.g., us-east, eu-west)

# Toggle Chat or Activity Feed depending on your use-case

# Click Create


# 3. ======================== Copy the Keys =======================

# After creating the app, you'll see:

# API Key → used in frontend (NEXT_PUBLIC_STREAM_API_KEY)

# Secret Key → used only in backend (STREAM_SECRET_KEY)

# App ID (optional in some SDKs)

